This tES/EEG/CTT/Vigilance experiment contains 19 unique participants (some repeated experiments).
Over a 70 min period EEG/ECG/EOG were recorded concurrently with a CTT task
where participants maintained a ball at the center of the screen.
and were periodically stimulated for 30 secs with combinations of 9 stimulation montages.
For the raw data please see: https://zenodo.org/record/4456079 
For methodological details please see corresponding article of the same name.

- Nigel Gebodh (May 26th, 2021)